20long-distance%20BFF.%20Their%20pictures%20showed%20up%20on%20my%20iPhone%20lockscreen%20as%20a%20%26quot%3BLive%20Activity%26quot%3B%20when%20the%20feature%20was%20enabled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20getting%20started%20to%20maintaining%20streaks%2C%20here's%20what%20my%2072%20hours%20on%20Yope%20looked%20like%20before%20I%20hit%20my%20deadline%20to%20file%20my%20first%20impressions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e07fdb4-6219-43d5-a578-c01bf155bd25%5C%22%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20get%20started%20if%20you%20already%20have%20a%20group%20in%20mind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20image%20of%20Yope%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb042eb8b41a9673f9fa71%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EYope%3B%20Jordan%20Hart%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EYope%20is%20straightforward%20and%20easy%20to%20use%20once%20you've%20downloaded%20the%20app.%20I%20created%20a%20profile%20and%20enabled%20Live%20Activities%20before%20making%20a%20group%20called%20%26quot%3BJordan's%20Besties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hard%20part%20was%20getting%20said%20besties%20to%20join%20the%20app%20to%20make%20it%20usable%20for%20me.%20Without%20them%2C%20I%20was%20in%20the%20private%20group%20alone%20with%20only%20myself%20to%20post%20pictures%20to%20the%20collaborative%20wall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20posts%20aren't%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20seen%20by%20users%20outside%20of%20the%20group%20chat%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20%26quot%3Bexplore%26quot%3B%20section.%20You%20can%20search%20for%20others%2C%20but%20you%20can%20only%20see%20their%20content%20if%20you're%20in%20a%20joint%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226fe0caab-df12-4c19-9568-e117d6b4a8b7%5C%22%3EI%20finally%20got%20my%20friends%20to%20join%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22composite%20image%20of%20Yope%20app%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C