t%20of%20Q%20System%20One%2C%20the%20first%20circuit-based%20commercial%20quantum%20computer%2C%20unveiled%20in%20January%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIBM's%20Condor%20chip%20is%20the%20company's%20most%20powerful%20in%20terms%20of%20its%20number%20of%20qubits.%20However%2C%20since%20its%20development%2C%20IBM%20has%20focused%20its%20approach%20on%20the%20quality%20of%20its%20gate%20operations%20and%20making%20its%20newer%20quantum%20chips%20modular%20so%20multiple%20smaller%2C%20less%20error-prone%20chips%20can%20be%20combined%20to%20make%20more%20powerful%20quantum%20computing%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECondor%2C%20the%20second-largest%20quantum%20processor%20ever%20made%2C%20was%20unveiled%20at%20the%20IBM%20Quantum%20Summit%202023%20on%20December%204%2C%202023.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20IBM%20debuted%20its%20Heron%20chip%2C%20a%20133-qubit%20processor%20with%20a%20lower%20error%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERob%20Schoelkopf%2C%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20scientist%20of%20Quantum%20Circuits%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20IBM%20has%20prioritized%20%26quot%3Berror%20mitigation%26quot%3B%20over%20traditional%20error%20correction%20approaches.%20While%20IBM%20has%20so%20far%20been%20successful%20in%20what%20Schoelkopf%20calls%20%26quot%3Bbrute%20force%20scaling%26quot%3B%20with%20this%20approach%2C%20he%20said%20the%20methodology%20will%20need%20to%20be%20modified%20in%20the%20long%20run%20for%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2275ae984a-7522-4fba-a1e0-0dc3cf949152%5C%22%3EWho%20leads%20the%20race%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESankar%20Das%20Sarma%2C%20a%20theoretical%20condensed%20matter%20physicist%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Maryland%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%20Ocelot%20chip%2C%20Google's%20Willow%2C%20and%20IBM's%20Condor%20use%20a%20%26quot%3Bmore%20conventional%26quot%3B%20superconducting%20approach%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fare-ionq-form-and-ibm-