BWho%20gives%20you%20these%20ideas%3F%20why%20will%20we%20welcome%20him%3F%20There%20is%20no%20offer%2C%20don't%20talk%20nonsense.%20No%20one%20other%20than%20Lalu%20(Yadav)%20ji%20and%20I%20is%20authorised%20to%20make%20offers%2C%20and%20no%20offer%20will%20be%20made%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rumours%20of%20behind-the-scenes%20outreach%20between%20JDU%20and%20RJD%20are%20playing%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20Mr%20Kumar's%20history%20of%20flip-flops%20across%20the%20political%20aisle.%20Once%20RJD%20founder%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20arch-political%20rival%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20tied%20up%20with%20RJD%20in%20the%202015%20state%20polls%20and%20the%20alliance%20scored%20a%20thumping%20win.%20Two%20years%20after%20the%20election%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20joined%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%20to%20return%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20JDU%20and%20BJP%20fought%20the%202020%20polls%20in%20alliance%2C%20but%20Mr%20Kumar%20made%20another%20flip-flop%20two%20years%20later%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20Opposition%20camp.%20In%202024%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20JDU%20chief%20made%20his%20latest%20switch%20and%20returned%20to%20the%20NDA.%20The%20BJP%20backed%20him%20as%20he%20took%20the%20oath%20for%20the%20ninth%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20few%20days%20have%20seen%20stormy%20exchanges%20between%20Mr%20Kumar%20and%20Mr%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20debate%20on%20Governor%20Arif%20Mohammed%20Khan's%20address%2C%20Mr%20Kumar%20thundered%20at%20the%20RJD%20leader%20and%20said%20he%20made%20Lalu%20Yadav%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20the%20people%20of%20Lalu%20Yadav's%20caste%20(Yadav)%20had%20refused%20to%20make%20him%20CM%2C%20but%20I%20supported%20him.%20I%20made%20your%20father%20(Lalu%20Yadav)%20CM%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%2C%20a%20key%20face%20of%20Janata%20Dal%20politics%20in%201990s%2C%20was%20Mr%20Yadav's