nd%20see%20what%20happens.%20Obviously%20expected%20a%20few%20blue%20shirts%2C%20great%20atmosphere%2C%20great%20ground.%20Going%20to%20be%20slightly%20different%20from%20what%20we%20got%20in%20Pakistan.%20We%20saw%20how%20India%20played%20and%20what%20they%20got%20out%20of%20it.%20Hope%20it%20slows%20down%20a%20bit%20later.%20Different%20guys%20have%20stepped%20up%20at%20different%20times.%20You%20want%20guys%20firing%20from%20the%20start%20and%20we%20have%20done%20that%2C%20as%20have%20India.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Matt%20Henry%20has%20been%20ruled%20out%2C%20we've%20got%20Nathan%20Smith%20coming%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Santner%20said%20at%20the%20toss.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20losing%20the%20toss%2C%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20insisted%20that%20he%20doesn't%20mind%20batting%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20here%20enough%2C%20batted%20first%20and%20bowled%20first%2C%20don't%20really%20mind%20batting%20second.%20It%20hasn't%20changed%20much%2C%20we've%20chased%20and%20won%20as%20well.%20It%20does%20give%20you%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%2C%20takes%20the%20toss%20away%20from%20the%20game.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20what%20matters%20is%20how%20well%20you%20want%20to%20play.%20That's%20what%20we've%20spoken%20about%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%2C%20not%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20toss%20and%20to%20just%20play%20well%2C%20that's%20what%20we've%20done%20and%20we%20have%20to%20do%20today%20as%20well.%20New%20Zealand%20have%20been%20a%20very%20good%20team%20over%20the%20past%20so%20many%20years%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20play%20good%20cricket%20in%20ICC%20tournaments.%20The%20challenge%20for%20us%20is%20to%20play%20well%20against%20them%20now.%20Same%20team%20for%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%20(Playing%20XI)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E(c)