be2fff9a3d266%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20living%20room%20in%20the%20reporter's%20suite.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20French%2C%20the%20director%20of%20hotel%20operations%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20when%20redesigning%20the%20suites%2C%20they%20aimed%20for%20an%20old-world%20European%20ambiance%20with%20modern%20comforts%20and%20luxury.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20teal%2C%20English%20wool%20carpeting%20filled%20the%20living%20room%20and%20bedroom.%20In%20the%20living%20room%2C%20a%20TV%20was%20across%20from%20a%20couch.%20The%20coffee%20table%20was%20tall%20enough%20for%20me%20to%20eat%20breakfast%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20room%20was%20a%20desk%20with%20a%20large%20leather%20chair%20in%20front%20of%20a%20wall%20of%20floor-to-ceiling%20windows.%20Working%20there%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20an%20exec.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDouble%20doors%20revealed%20the%20bedroom%20%E2%80%94%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20comfortable%20mattresses%20I've%20ever%20slept%20on.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223413%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Inside%20a%20light%20blue%20room%20with%20a%20wooden%20victorian%20bedframe%20topped%20with%20white%20linens%20sandwiched%20between%20two%20wooden%20nightstands%20with%20lamps%20on%20each%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67a50b73bfebcc4d029e1716%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bed%20in%20the%20reporter's%20suite.%3Cp%3EJoey%20Hadden%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20said%20they%20considered%20a%20variety%20of%20luxury%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emattress%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20suites%20and%20customized%20their%20top%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20handpicked%20and%