m%C3%A9%20that%20landed%20him%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20role%20building%20security%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrior%20to%20Microsoft%2C%20Masrani%20studied%20IT%2C%20got%20a%20Master's%20in%20computer%20science%2C%20and%20worked%20at%20AWS.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20data%20experience%20and%20security%20knowledge%20are%20needed%20to%20transition%20to%20cybersecurity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBreaking%20into%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-into-cybersecurity-career-job-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecybersecurity%20field%20can%20be%20a%20challenge%20for%20some%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%2036-year-old%20Ankit%20Masrani%20stumbled%20into%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Seattle-based%20Microsoft%20employee%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20while%20he%20had%20plans%20to%20become%20a%20software%20engineer%2C%20he%20didn't%20expect%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-cybersecurity-jobs-high-demand-ai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20in%20the%20security%20space%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Now%2C%20he%20develops%20sovereignty%20controls%20for%20the%20tech%20giant's%20security%20platform%2C%20ensuring%20sensitive%20customer%20information%20remains%20within%20geographic%20boundaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20studying%20information%20technology%20in%20college%20and%20working%20in%20roles%20building%20software%20systems%2C%20Masrani%20came%20to%20the%20US%20to%20get%20a%20Master's%20degree%20in%20computer%20science.%20After%20completing%20a%20six-month%20co-op%20internship%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAWS%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20he%20was%20in%20school%2C%20he%20converted%20to%20a%20full-time%20employee%2C%20where%20he%20focused%20on%20secur