were%20also%20killed.%20The%20fighting%20has%20left%20large%20parts%20of%20Latakia%20without%20electricity%20and%20drinking%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESOHR%20reported%20that%20Syrian%20security%20forces%20executed%20at%20least%20162%20Alawites%20in%20%26quot%3Bfield%20executions%26quot%3B%20in%20Latakia%20province%2C%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Assad%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20sect.%20The%20Syrian%20Interior%20Ministry%20acknowledged%20%26quot%3Bindividual%20violations%26quot%3B%20along%20the%20coast%20and%20vowed%20to%20take%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clashes%2C%20which%20erupted%20Thursday%2C%20are%20a%20major%20challenge%20to%20Syria's%20new%20rulers%2C%20who%20took%20power%20three%20months%20ago%20after%20removing%20Assad.%20The%20government%20claims%20it%20was%20responding%20to%20attacks%20from%20remnants%20of%20Assad's%20forces%20and%20downplayed%20the%20killings%20as%20isolated%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Are%20The%20Alawites%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alawites%20are%20a%20religious%20minority%20in%20Syria%2C%20constituting%20about%2012%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population.%20Originating%20from%20Shia%20Islam%2C%20they%20have%20distinct%20beliefs%20and%20rituals.%20Historically%2C%20the%20Alawites%20have%20been%20concentrated%20in%20Syria's%20coastal%20regions%2C%20especially%20in%20Latakia%20and%20Tartus%20provinces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Assad%20family%2C%20which%20ruled%20Syria%20for%20over%20five%20decades%20until%20December%202024%2C%20belongs%20to%20the%20Alawite%20sect.%20During%20their%20rule%2C%20Alawites%20held%20significant%20positions%20in%20the%20military%20and%20government%2C%20leading%20to%20perceptions%20of%20preferential%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Are%20They%20Being%20Killed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Assad's%20ousting%2C%20armed%20Sunni%20factions%2C%20reportedly%20loyal%20to%20the%20new%20government%2C%20launched%20revenge%20killings%20against