20Siamese%20tabby%20cat.%3Cp%3EPurryfuls%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246cfbca3-500f-49e1-8b79-add6842f6e2e%5C%22%3EPlushies%20are%20hot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20boom%20in%20plushie%20sales%20among%20adults%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlushies%20are%20%26quot%3Bhot%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Benway%2C%20the%20senior%20tech%20and%20gaming%20analyst%20at%20Mintel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplushies-millennials-gen-z-hooked-toy-sales-happiness-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20BI%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20Mintel's%20Traditional%20Toys%20and%20Games%20report%2C%20published%20in%20October%202024%2C%20Benway%20said%20that%20plushies%20were%20particularly%20in%20demand%2C%20with%20sales%20growing%20significantly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20attribute%20plushie%20popularity%20to%20millennials%20clinging%20onto%20their%20youth%2C%20but%20others%20think%20it's%20because%20there%20is%20less%20judgment%20about%20alternative%20interests%20and%20hobbies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%20said%20she%20wasn't%20aware%20of%20this%20when%20launching%20Purryfuls%2C%20but%20it's%20the%20age%20group%20she's%20targeting.%20She%20isn't%20surprised%20that%20Gen%20Zers%20and%20millennials%20are%20turning%20toward%20stuffed%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20still%20remember%20my%20teddy%20bear%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20the%20first%20comforting%20device%20that%20I%20had%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20key%20mission%20here%20was%20just%20to%20make%20something%20that%20would%20bring%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20calm%20to%20someone's%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurke%20realized%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20things%20that%20stressed%20her%20out%20%E2%80%94%20fights%20with%20insurance%20companies%2C%20DMV%20bills%2C%20unexpected%20expenses%20from%20leaking%20pipes%20%E2%80%94%20would%20probably%20be%20stressing%20others%20out%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20meant%20to%20be%20a%20little%20moment%20of%20calm%2C%20a%20little%20moment%20of%20joy%20in%20your%20day%2C%20so%20that%20you%20can%20take%20a%20break%2C%26quot%3B%20Burke%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20isn't%20to%20replace%20real%20pets%20but%20to%20be%20there%20when%20you%20need%20their%20comfort%2C%20and%20they%20have%20better%20things%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20several%20different%20settings%2C%20including%20a%20sleep%20mode%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Purryful%20purrs%20quietly%20for%2010%20minutes%20to%20help%20you%20drift%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2210ab56c6-b829-4e28-98de-ca405f542de4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPurring%20is%20healing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPurring%20is%20thought%20to%20be%20healing%20for%20cats%20and%20a%20sign%20of%20happiness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Margaret%20Atwood's%20%26quot%3BMaddAddam%26quot%3B%20trilogy%2C%20an%20idealistic%2C%20genetically%20spliced%20humanoid%20species%20has%20coopted%20the%20cat's%20purr%20to%20heal%20physical%20wounds.%20This%20may%20not%20just%20be%20science%20fiction%2C%20though%2C%20because%20academic%20research%20suggests%20purring%20could%20be%20good%20for%20us%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20article%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cabidigitallibrary.org%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1079%2Fhai.2021.0006%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman-Animal%20Interaction%20Bulletin%3C%2Fa%3E%20journal%20in%202023%20featured%20a%20small%20study%20of%2065%20respondents%20of%20different%20ages%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20had%20pet%20cats%20for%20varying%20amounts%20of%20time.%20The%20cat%20owners%20reported%20that%20their%20cats'%20purrs%20had%20a%20relaxing%20and%20calming%20effect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20authors%20noted%20the%20function%20of%20a%20cat's%20purr%20is%20not%20entirely%20understood%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC6051063%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20research%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20mechanical%20vibrations%20have%20been%20shown%20to%20promote%20self-healing%20in%20humans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cabidigitallibrary.org%2Fdoi%2Fpdf%2F10.1079%2Fhai.2021.0009%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20another%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20looked%20at%20the%20impact%20of%20a%20pet%20cat%20on%20mental%20wellbeing%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%20owners%20described%20their%20moggy's%20purrs%20as%20grounding%20and%20comforting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-are-the-most-stressed-out-2015-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMillennials%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fremote-work-fueling-gen-z-job-anxiety-stress-mental-health-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZoomers%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20both%20been%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Banxious%26quot%3B%20generations%2C%20and%20Burke%20wants%20Purryfuls%20to%20be%20there%20to%20help%20if%20it%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20that%20I%20want%20to%20say%20that%20things%20are%20harder%20for%20one%20generation%20over%20another%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20probably%20just%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20I%20do%20feel%20that%20now%20what%20we're%20getting%20is%20people%20saying%2C%20no%2C%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20follow%20the%20path%20you%20prescribed%20for%20me.%20I%20am%20going%20to%20make%20my%20choices%20for%20myself%20based%20on%20what%20I%20like%2C%20and%20what%20feels%20right%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Burke%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20something%20I%20can%20really%20relate%20to%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20exactly%20what%20I%20did.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplushies-purring-entrepreneur-purryfuls-adult-toys-anxious-millennials-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741