eral%20teams%20from%202020%20to%202022%2C%20including%20business%20and%20legal%20affairs%20as%20well%20as%20government%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20be%20very%20clear%20that%20we%20do%20think%20excellence%20in%20having%20the%20colleagues%20around%20you%20is%20super%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Netflix%20co-CEO%20Greg%20Peters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F24182520%2Fnetflix-co-ceo-memo-ads-subscription-price-decoder-podcast-interview%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20Decoder%20podcast%20last%20year.%20%26quot%3BTo%20the%20degree%20the%20business%20evolves%20or%20moves%20and%20we%20think%20there's%20a%20change%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20made%2C%20we%20will%20make%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d5f69858-18dd-436e-a261-8c16d4a6cd6c%5C%22%3ENetflix%20has%20a%20high%20level%20of%20feedback%20and%20transparency%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20to%20handling%20performance%20issues%2C%20Soumar%C3%A9%20said%20he%20admired%20Netflix's%20culture%20of%20transparent%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix's%20culture%20memo%20says%20%26quot%3Bextraordinary%20candor%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20key%20value%20in%20assembling%20a%20%26quot%3Bdream%20team.%26quot%3B%20And%20rather%20than%20quarterly%20or%20annually%2C%20feedback%20should%20happen%20daily%2C%20%26quot%3Blike%20brushing%20your%20teeth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223579%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Netflix%20co-CEO%20Greg%20Peters%2C%20wearing%20a%20green%20jacket%20and%20beige%20sweater%2C%20at%20the%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%202%2C%26quot%3B%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20a%20pink%20wall.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb27d4b8b41a9673fa020b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222684%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20think%20excellence%20in%20having%20the%20colleagues%20around%20you%20is%20super%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Netflix%20co-CEO