3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20soldier%20climbing%20down%20from%20the%20front%20of%20a%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tank.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6698104afb2b6bedb05808c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Abrams%20is%20one%20of%20only%20a%20few%20Western-provided%20tanks%20that%20Ukraine%20is%20fielding.%3Cp%3E47th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20via%20Telegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20while%20we%20have%20the%20equipment%2C%20we%20may%20be%20unable%20to%20use%20it%20due%20to%20maintenance%20constraints.%20This%20is%20not%20about%20new%20supplies%20but%20about%20sustaining%20existing%20equipment%2C%26quot%3B%20Rakhmanin%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20sent%2031%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tanks%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202023.%20The%20following%20summer%2C%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20said%20that%20this%20number%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-faces-same-problem-with-f16s-as-abrams-tanks-zelenskyy-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewouldn't%20be%20enough%20to%20make%20a%20difference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20case.%20The%20Abrams%20features%20a%20powerful%20gas%20turbine%20engine%20and%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20requiring%20more%20maintenance%20than%20other%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20contrast%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20sent%20over%20300%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-made-abrams-bradleys-taking-hits-but-surviving-in-ukraine-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBradleys%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20more%20than%20400%20Strykers%2C%20and%20hundreds%20of%20other%20armored%20vehicles%20to%20Kyiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComplicating%20matters%20is%20the%20fact%20Ukraine%20has%20also%20received%20Germany's%20Leopard%202%20and%20Britain's%20Challenger%202%20tanks%2C%20which%20each%20require%20their%20own%20spare%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Australian%20government%20said%20in%20October%20that%20it%20planned%20to%20send%20nearly%2050%20of%20its%20aging%20M1A1%20Abranks%20tanks%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20a%20move%20that%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustralia-boost-ukraine-abrams-tank-force-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20double%20the%20size%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Kyiv's%20existing%20inventory.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225472%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20M1A1%20Abrams%20tank%20in%20Germany%20on%20May%2012%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66687e18e07904901817bc45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Abrams%20is%20an%20aging%20tank%20but%20can%20still%20deliver%20a%20tremendous%20amount%20of%20combat%20strength.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%20photo%20by%20Spc.%20Christian%20Carrillo%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20unclear%20when%20those%20additional%20tanks%20might%20arrive%2C%20meaning%20that%20Ukraine%20has%20had%20to%20be%20somewhat%20conservative%20with%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbradley-fighting-vehicles-prove-worth-ukraine-short-on-abrams-tanks-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimited%20number%20of%20Abrams%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lack%20of%20spare%20parts%20will%20only%20increase%20the%20risk.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oryxspioenkop.com%2F2022%2F02%2Fattack-on-europe-documenting-ukrainian.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOryx%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20open-source%20intelligence%20site%20that%20tracks%20war%20losses%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20at%20least%2019%20of%20Ukraine's%20Abrams%20have%20been%20damaged%20or%20destroyed.%20BI%20is%20unable%20to%20independently%20verify%20these%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20much%20of%20the%20war%2C%20it%20had%20been%20the%20US%20policy%20that%20when%20American-provided%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-helps-ukraine-fix-busted-artillery-over-phone-often-battle-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20equipment%20suffered%20damage%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20would%20be%20transported%20out%20of%20the%20country%20to%20NATO%20soil%2C%20like%20Poland.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20timely%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERakhmanin%20said%20the%20US%20has%20always%20had%20a%20strict%20policy%20about%20allowing%20its%20military%20hardware%20to%20be%20repaired%20inside%20Ukraine%2C%20which%20will%20only%20get%20worse%20under%20the%20Trump%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20leads%20to%20absurd%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20Rakhmanin%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20we%20might%20have%20a%20tank%20that%20is%20fully%20operational%20except%20for%20a%20small%20missing%20part.%20We%20cannot%20manufacture%20it%20because%20we%20lack%20the%20blueprints%20and%20authorization.%20We%20also%20do%20not%20have%20the%20necessary%20expertise%20to%20produce%20such%20components%20independently.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bradley%20Ukraine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a7b9e76979d7371823d76b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20has%20received%20significantly%20more%20Bradley%20fighting%20vehicles%20than%20Abrams%20tanks.%3Cp%3EAnadolu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20tank%20sits%20idle%20in%20a%20parking%20lot%20while%20we%20wait%20for%20months%20to%20receive%20the%20spare%20part%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20US%20could%20allow%20European%20countries%20to%20buy%20and%20send%20spare%20parts%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20it's%20unclear%20if%20this%20will%20be%20authorized.%20If%20it%20isn't%2C%20Kyiv%20wil