ng%20to%20police%2C%20Pankaj%20and%20Saurabh%20were%20returning%20from%20a%20temple%20in%20Kashmiri%20Gate%20on%20March%201%20morning.%20Saurabh%20was%20at%20the%20wheel%20and%20the%20car%20was%20at%20high%20speed.%20Around%206%20am%2C%20the%20car%20hit%20Rishal's%20bicycle%20at%20Rohini's%20KN%20Katju%20Marg.%20Such%20was%20the%20impact%20that%20the%2019-year-old%20was%20swept%20off%20his%20feet%20and%20landed%20on%20the%20car's%20windscreen.%20His%20cycle%20was%20dragged%20under%20the%20car%20before%20it%20eventually%20sped%20away%2C%20leaving%20the%20youngster%20dead%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Police%20Tracked%20Down%20Killer%20Car%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20identify%20the%20car%20that%20hit%20Rishal%2C%20police%20scanned%20footage%20from%20more%20than%20150%20CCTV%20cameras.%20After%20piecing%20together%20the%20sequence%20of%20events%2C%20police%20tracked%20down%20the%20car%20to%20a%20garage%20in%20Haryana's%20Panipat.%20The%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20the%20windscreen%20and%20bonnet%20of%20the%20blue%20Hyundai%20Venue%20car%20were%20damaged%20in%20the%20crash.%20And%20the%20accused%20tried%20to%20fix%20the%20vehicle%20and%20destroy%20evidence.%20But%20before%20this%20could%20be%20done%2C%20the%20police%20tracked%20down%20and%20seized%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Dream%20Journey%20Cut%20Short%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20resident%20of%20Budh%20Vihar%2C%20Rishal%20Singh%20has%20four%20siblings%20--%20three%20sisters%2C%20who%20are%20married%2C%20and%20a%20younger%20brother%2C%20a%20Class%208%20student.%20His%20father%20works%20as%20a%20labourer%20in%20a%20utensils%20factory.%20Rishal%20would%20make%20about%20Rs%2010%2C000%20by%20distributing%20newspapers.%20Besides%20supporting%20the%20family%20income%2C%20he%20would%20use%20the%20money%20for%20his%20education.%20The%2019-year-old%20was%20a%20first-year%20student%20at%20Delhi%20University's%20School%20of%20Open%20Learning.%20The%