0me%20some%20quiet%20time.%20We%20have%20two%20young%20children%2C%20so%20I%20can%20%26quot%3Bgo%20to%20work%26quot%3B%20without%20being%20in%20the%20main%20house%20with%20all%20the%20chaos%20and%20noise.%20It's%20truly%20been%20a%20game%20changer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232382e90-5cfa-45c3-8cb7-e2393882bf87%5C%22%3EThe%20construction%20process%20was%20simple%20and%20fast%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20it's%20separate%20from%20the%20main%20house%2C%20the%20home%20office%20is%20the%20most%20beautiful%20room%20on%20the%20property%20%E2%80%94%20everyone%20who%20sees%20it%20is%20completely%20wowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20all%20out%20with%20super-tall%2C%20dramatic%20ceilings%20and%20a%20massive%20wall%20of%20windows.%20We%20also%20built%20a%20fire%20pit%20in%20front%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20real%20focal%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228064%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Mauldin's%20working%20space.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8b83369253ccddf986430%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMauldin's%20working%20space.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Justin%20Mauldin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20decided%20to%20build%20an%20ADU%2C%20COVID%20made%20it%20difficult%20to%20get%20bids%2C%20materials%2C%20and%20reliable%20contractors%2C%20so%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmycabin-us-tiny-homes-prefab-pads-factory-cost-size-delivery-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-fabricated%3C%2Fa%3E%20option%20seemed%20like%20the%20best%20choice.%20I%20went%20with%20Studio%20Shed%2C%20a%20Denver-based%20company%20that%20builds%20the%20structure%20in%20their%20warehouse%20and%20then%20ships%20it%20to%20be%20assembled%20on-site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20simple%2C%20like%20building%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flego-success-inflation-proof-toy-industry-2