nd%20paid%20about%20%24500%20to%20install.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20was%20built%20and%20finished%20quickly.%20The%20ADU%20was%20delivered%20on%20February%201%2C%202021%2C%20and%20completed%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fb99fce-e4d2-430f-8220-e8e8a1b24684%5C%22%3EThe%20ADU%20allowed%20our%20family%20of%204%20to%20live%20more%20comfortably%20in%20a%20smaller%20house%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGiven%20the%20price%20of%20our%20home%2C%20it's%20clear%20we're%20not%20in%20a%20fancy%2C%20McMansion-filled%20neighborhood.%20Most%20homes%20here%20are%201950s%20bungalows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20first%20moved%20into%20our%20home%2C%20instead%20of%20following%20the%20common%20trend%20%E2%80%94%20where%20people%20tear%20down%20these%20homes%20to%20build%20new%20constructions%20%E2%80%94%20we%20took%20the%20opposite%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20wanted%20to%20preserve%20the%20character%2C%20so%20we%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20renovations%3A%20replacing%20the%20siding%2C%20repainting%2C%20completely%20redoing%20the%20interior%2C%20and%20reworking%20the%20landscaping.%20I%20think%20the%20neighbors%20really%20appreciated%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228014%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20interior%20of%20Justin%20Mauldin's%20ADU.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c8b7c5b1834fe311664546%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226010%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMauldin%20runs%20his%20company%20from%20his%20home%20office.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Justin%20Mauldin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20have%20two%20girls%2C%20so%20a%201%2C200-square-foot%20home%20with%20just%20one%20bathroom%20can%20be%20a%20challenge%2C%20especially%20when%20we%20have%20visitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20we'd%20love%20a%20bigger%20home%2C%20but%20with%20prices%20still%20unaffordable%2C%20it's%20tough.%20When%20we%20bought%20our%20home%2C%20our%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftodays-mortgage-rates-wednesday-5-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0was%20locked%20at%202.5%25%20%E2%80%94%20rates%20now%20are%20much%20higher.%20Most%20homes%20in%20desirable%20areas%20are%20in%20the%20%241.5%20million%20range%2C%20and%20with%20the%20high%20property%20taxes%20here%2C%20it's%20just%20not%20realistic.%20We%20could%20not%20afford%20a%20place%20in%20Austin%20now%20without%20doubling%20or%20tripling%20our%20housing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20we're%20happy%20with%20our%20place%2C%20and%20maybe%20we'll%20add%20a%20bathroom%20one%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229f065def-943a-4cb9-a972-d7445f582a39%5C%22%3EADUs%20are%20becoming%20popular%20in%20Austin%2C%20and%20I%20can%20see%20why%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAustin%20has%20a%20housing%20crisis%2C%20yet%20people%20still%20want%20to%20live%20here%20and%20continue%20moving%20to%20the%20city.%20I%20think%20creative%20solutions%20like%20ADUs%20are%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20city%20has%20made%20it%20much%20easier%20to%20add%20ADUs%20to%20properties%2C%20especially%20the%20type%20I%20built%2C%20which%20is%20under%20200%20square%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20with%20a%20permit%2C%20you%20could%20divide%20a%20quarter-acre%20or%20smaller%20property%20into%20two%20lots%20%E2%80%94%20one%20for%20your%20main%20home%20and%20the%20other%20for%20an%20ADU%2C%20often%20for%20uses%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairbnb-host-rental-spare-bedroom-side-hustle-income-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAirbnb%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20now%2C%20with%20relaxed%20regulations%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20add%20a%20small%20structure%20in%20the%20back%20of%20your%20property%20without%20needing%20a%20permit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228064%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Mauldin's%20office%2C%20featuring%20his%20computer%20and%20motorcycle.%5C%22%20c