o-rent'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPotts%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20home%20built%20by%20his%20parents%20in%20Fort%20Worth%2C%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20remember%20walking%20through%20and%20seeing%20the%20process%20as%20an%20eight-%2C%20nine-year-old%20boy%2C%20and%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BEven%20at%20that%20age%2C%20I%20liked%20seeing%20something%20start%20from%20scratch%20and%20become%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20followed%20in%20his%20parent's%20footsteps%20and%20built%20the%20three%20homes%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20Mindy%20have%20resided%20in%20over%20the%20past%20few%20decades.%20The%20process%20was%20satisfying%20for%20Potts%20%E2%80%94%20and%20economical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22brannon%20potts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb416d585f1dff88b18588%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPotts%20owns%20a%20mixture%20of%20single-family%20and%20multi-family%20properties.%20He%20builds%20and%20designs%20each%20of%20his%20rentals.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brannon%20Potts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20noticed%20a%20pattern%20when%20I%20was%20building%20my%20houses%3A%20Every%20time%20we%20built%2C%20it%20had%20equity%20over%20and%20above%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20build%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20like%2C%20well%2C%20then%20why%20don't%20I%20do%20it%20with%20rentals%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20he%20tackled%20his%20first%20two%20build-to-rent%20projects%3A%20a%20beach%20house%20that%20he%20and%20Mindy%20converted%20into%20a%20short-term%20rental%20and%20a%20fourplex%20that%20they%20filled%20with%20long-term%20tenants.%20Both%20projects%20wrapped%20in%202021%20and%20immediately%20started%20generating%20cash%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20love%20building%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20able%20to%20put%20my%20fingerprint%20on%20a%20property%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20for%20me%20it%20was%20natural%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20really%20proud%20of%20how%20I%20finished%20them%20out.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20built%20them%20with%20the%20idea%20that%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20always%20think%20worst%20case%20scenario%20%E2%80%94%20if%20times%20were%20tough%2C%20would%20we%20be%20good%20to%20live%20there%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%202021%20and%202024%2C%20Potts%20built%20one%20to%20two%20properties%20a%20year%20and%20expanded%20to%2010%20doors.%20As%20of%20March%202025%2C%20he%20has%20two%20more%20under%20construction%20and%20expects%20to%20have%20a%20total%20of%2012%20completed%20doors%20by%20mid-2025.%20They're%20all%20long-term%20rentals%20except%20the%20beach%20house.%20BI%20viewed%20owner%20statements%20to%20verify%20his%20property%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20long-term%20rentals%2C%20he%20said%20he%20cash-flows%2C%20on%20average%2C%20%24330%20a%20month%20per%20door.%20He%20doesn't%20think%20he'd%20get%20close%20to%20those%20numbers%20if%20he%20bought%20pre-existing%20properties%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20resale%20market%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20harder%20to%20pencil%20out%20and%20work%20financially.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPotts%2C%20who%20also%20runs%20a%20property%20management%20company%2C%20expects%20to%20hit%20financial%20independence%20once%20he%20gets%20to%2020%20doors%2C%20which%20he%20plans%20to%20do%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years%20and%20before%20turning%2060.%20At%20that%20point%2C%20he%20can%20stop%20working%2C%20relax%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20and%20spend%20more%20time%20with%20his%20three%20kids.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20important%20outfit%20decision%20he%20makes%20each%20morning%20helps%20him%20to%20stay%20focused%20on%20his%20long-term%20goal%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20wear%20Hawaiian%20shirts%20every%20single%20day.%20It's%20a%20reminder%20to%20me%20that%20my%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20to%20financial%20freedom%20and%20live%20life%20on%20the%20beach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9920099-2808-43ac-b05e-e6489bc1d145%5C%22%3E3%20key%20components%20of%20the%20build-to-rent%20strategy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPotts%20believes%20that%20with%20the%20right%20builder%2C%20anyone%20can%20replicate%20his%20build-to-rent%20strategy.%20He%20broke%20down%20the%20main%20components%20of%20a%20successful%20project%20and%20how%20he%20budgets%20to%20ensure%20immediate%20cash%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20The%20land.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPotts%2C%20who%20mainly%20uses%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mls.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMLS%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20find%20land%2C%20is%20looking%20for%20infill%20lots%20that%20are%20relatively%20flat.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20grade%20to%20them%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20to%20put%20in%20retaining%20walls%2C%20which%20add%20cost%20to%20the%20lot%20development%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20looking%20to%20spend%20about%2015%25%20of%20the%20project's%20cost%20on%20the%20land%20and%20whatever%20it%20may%20take%20to%20prepare%20it%20for%20a%20home%20foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20lots%20I'm%20looking%20at%20are%20in%20that%20%2415%2C000%20to%20%2420%2C000%20per%20door%20range%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20if%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20fourplex%2C%20I'm%20trying%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20that%20%2460%2C000%20range%2C%20a%20triplex%20would%20be%20in%20the%20%2445%2C000%20range%2C%20and%20%2415%2C000%20to%20%2420%2C000%20for%20a%20single-family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22brannon%20potts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb4220b8b41a9673fa084b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223495%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPotts%20owns%20one%20short-term%20rental%2C%20a%20beach%20house%20in%20Port%20Aransas%20that%20his%20daughter%20named%20%26quot%3BTurtle%20Ransas.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brannon%20Potts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20The%20build.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPotts%2C%20who%20buys%20and%20builds%20in%20Fort%20Worth%2C%20keeps%20his%20building%20cost%20at%20about%20%24120%20per%20square%20foot.%20The%20process%20from%20start%20to%20finish%20takes%20about%20six%20months%20for%20a%20single-family%20home%20and%20nine%20months%20for%20a%20multi-family.%20Though%20the%20timeline%20may%20look%20different%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BEvery%20area%20is%20different.%20It%20just%20depends%20on%20the%20regulations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20pays%20close%20attention%20to%20the%20rent%20prices%20in%20his%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20my%20rents%20and%20I%20can%20reverse%20engineer%20it%20using%20the%201%25%20rule%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20if%20I%20know%20rents%20are%20going%20to%20be%20%242%2C100%2C%20can%20I%20build%20it%20for%20%24210%2C000%20or%20less%3F%20If%20I%20can%2C%20then%20I%20know%20it%20generally%20will%20cash%20flow%20with%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20money%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20uses%20the%20same%20rule%20with%20his%20multi-families.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20a%20triplex%20rents%20for%20%241%2C750%20per%20unit%2C%20the%20total%20rent%20is%20%245%2C250%2C%20so%20his%20budget%20for%20the%20build%20is%20about%20%24520%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20financing%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20pay%20cash%20upfront%20for%20the%20lot%2C%20we%20use%20that%20as%20collateral%20for%20the%20build%2C%20and%20then%20we're%20getting%20a%20construction%20loan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20then%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20we're%20getting%20a%20permanent%2030-year%20mortgage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20The%20tenants.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPotts%20hasn't%20had%20much%20difficulty%20renting%20in%20Fort%20Worth%2C%20which%20he%20describes%20as%20a%20growing%20area%20that'll%20only%20grow%20more%20when%20Amazon%20completes%20its%20regional%20distribution%20center.%20One%20of%20his%20rentals%20is%20less%20than%20a%20mile%20from%20the%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMulti-families%20tend%20to%20be%20trickier%20to%20fill%20than%20single-families.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20first%20open%20it%20up%2C%20just%20like%20an%20apartment%20complex%2C%20if%20you've%20got%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20units%20available%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time%20filling%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20challenge%20is%20just%20at%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20filling%20out%20all%20the%20units.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20doesn't%20want%20leases%20ending%20all%20in%20the%20same%20month%20to%20avoid%20potentially%20losing%20multiple%20tenants%20at%20once%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20we%20stagger%20when%20those%20renewals%20come%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222646%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22brannon%20potts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb42d2b8b41a9673fa088b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221985%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPotts%20wears%20Hawaiin%20shirts%20to%20remind%20himself%20of%20his%20goal%3A%20To%20retire%20early%20and%20live%20on%20the%20beach.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brannon%20Potts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20completed%2010%20rentals%2C%20Potts%20is%20confident%20that%20whenever%20he%20starts%20a%20new%20project%2C%20it%20will%20immediately%20generate%20at%20least%20a%20couple%20hundred%20dollars%20a%20month%20in%20cash%20flow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20do%20them%20unless%20they%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20buy%20a%20negative%20cash%20flow%20property.%20I'm%20still%20a%20banker%20at%20heart.%20I'm%20still%20very%20conservative%2C%20so%20I%20had%20a%20threshold.%20I%20wanted%20cash%20flow%20of%20at%20least%20%24200%20a%20door.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20general%20rule%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20more%20doors%20on%20the%20land%2C%20the%20more%20money%20it%20produces%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20but%20you%20can%20think%20beyond%20traditional%20%26quot%3Bdoors%26quot%3B%20to%20maximize%20revenue.%20For%20one%20of%20his%20projects%20that%20he%20was%20hoping%20to%20turn%20into%20a%20fourplex%2C%20city%20regulations%20required%20him%20to%20build%20a%20triplex.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20enough%20space%20to%20build%20four%20storage%20units%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20property%2C%20which%20he%20rents%20to%20his%20tenants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ended%20up%20building%20those%20four%20storage%20units%20for%20less%20than%20%2420%2C000%20total%2C%20and%20I%20rent%20those%20out%20at%20%2455%20per%2010-by-10%20%5Bfoot%5D%20storage%20unit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20generate%20another%20%24220%20in%20revenue%20off%20of%20those%20storage%20units%20on%20the%20same%20piece%20of%20dirt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20important%20as%20it%20is%20to%20understand%20your%20numbers%20in%20a%20build-to-rent%2C%20relationships%20matter%20just%20as%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20leveraging%20all%20these%20relationships%20you%20have.%20For%20me%2C%20it's%20the%20builder%2C%20banker%2C%20different%20contractors%20that%20I%20know%2C%20and%20a%20network%20of%20people%20who%20know%20what%20I'm%20looking%20for%20in%20properties%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Potts.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20relationships%20as%20much%20as%20it%20is%20numbers.%20You%20need%20both.%20You%20have%20to%20have%20your%20numbers%20right%2C%20but%20you%20also%20need%20those%20relationships%20to%20make%20it%20all%20come%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-shares-his-key-to-generating-cash-flow-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741507381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb43c9585f1dff88b18630%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22