20say%20people%20can%20do%20to%20prepare%20for%20a%20possible%20recession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2266b9e37c-0953-4228-9713-3c2d65440634%5C%22%3E1.%20Do%20not%20panic!%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20people%20scan%20the%20headlines%2C%20fear%20can%20be%20a%20powerful%20motivator%20to%20take%20drastic%20measures.%20But%20it's%20important%20not%20to%20act%20impulsively%20or%20be%20overly%20emotional%20about%20your%20plan%20and%20the%20actions%20you%20take%20that%20could%20impact%20your%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGina%20Bolvin%2C%20president%20of%20Bolvin%20Wealth%20Management%20Group%2C%20said%20because%20GDP%20data%20is%20backward-looking%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20the%20economy%20will%20emerge%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Frecession-vs-depression%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20recession%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20we%20even%20learn%20one%20has%20officially%20occurred.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20investment%20perspective%2C%20Blovin%20stressed%20that%20long-term%20investors%20should%20keep%20buying%20assets%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20lower%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20only%20change%20to%20your%20portfolio%20should%20be%20to%20confirm%20its%20diversified%20and%20you%20can%20weather%20the%20storm%20in%20good%20times%20or%20bad%2C%26quot%3B%20Bolvin%20said.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20panic.%20The%20headlines%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20change%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20specific%20investment%20considerations%2C%20stocks%20are%20often%20more%20volatile%20during%20a%20recession.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20shield%20your%20portfolio%20from%20big%20swings%20in%20equities%2C%20this%20could%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20increase%20your%20holdings%20of%20things%20like%20ultra-safe%20US%20Treasury%20bills%2C%20Lisa%20Featherngill%2C%20national%20director%20of%20wealth%20planning%20at%20Comerica%20Wealth%20Management%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EImportantly%2C%20if%20you're%20invested%20for%20a%20long-term%20goal%2C%20such%20as%20retirement%2C%20don't%20panic%20and%20sell%20into%20a%20tumbling%20market.%20While%20dips%20occur%2C%20the%20stock%20market's%20path%20over%20the%20decades%20has%20been%20consistently%20up%20and%20to%20the%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22822712b8-9016-4e62-96b9-059fcda10ad7%5C%22%3E2.%20Build%20an%20emergency%20fund%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBrett%20Panziera%2C%20CFP%2C%20associate%20director%20of%20financial%20planning%20at%20EP%20Wealth%20Advisors%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20crucial%20to%20build%20and%20maintain%20a%20cash%20reserve%20that%20can%20cover%20non-discretionary%20expenses%20in%20the%20event%20that%20you%20lose%20your%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20cash%20reserve%20prevents%20having%20to%20withdraw%20from%20invested%20assets%20that%20might%20be%20trading%20at%20a%20lower%20value%20due%20to%20a%20market%20decline.%20Essentially%2C%20without%20an%20adequate%20emergency%20fund%2C%20you%20risk%20selling%20stocks%20at%20low%20prices%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20outside%20of%20a%20recession%2C%20you%20should%20aim%20to%20have%20an%20amount%20of%20cash%20on%20hand%20to%20fund%20at%20least%206%20months%20of%20your%20expenses%2C%20or%20if%20you%20are%20retired%20and%20don't%20have%20employment%20income%20to%20support%20your%20spending%2C%20perhaps%20up%20to%202%20or%203%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Panziera%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20investments%20need%20time%20to%20recover%20when%20the%20market%20is%20down%20and%20this%20can%20potentially%20take%20years%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222a29faac-09e1-42e1-a79e-6c59768147c5%5C%22%3E3.%20Review%20your%20budget%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnderstanding%20your%20monthly%20spending%20is%20critical.%20According%20to%20Panziera%2C%20it's%20also%20key%20to%20knowing%20where%20you%20can%20cut%20back%20if%20you%20lose%20your%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%