nomic%20slowdown%2C%20Callahan%20recommends%20you%20prioritize%20paying%20down%20debt%2C%20as%20it%20can%20quickly%20grow%20if%20you%20miss%20payments%20due%20to%20lost%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEspecially%20in%20today's%20interest%20rate%20environment%2C%20where%20average%20credit%20card%20interest%20is%20around%2020%25%2C%20credit%20card%20debt%20will%20quickly%20balloon%20and%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20recover%20from%2C%26quot%3B%20Callahan%20said.%20%26quot%3BPaying%20down%20debt%20will%20boost%20your%20financial%20stability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFeatherngill%2C%20the%20wealth%20planner%20from%20Comerica%2C%20recommends%20paying%20down%20debts%20with%20the%20highest%20interest%20rate%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20an%20investment%2C%20repaying%20debt%20is%20like%20earning%20a%20rate%20of%20return%20equal%20to%20the%20interest%20rate%20on%20the%20debt%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20if%20you%20have%20a%20credit%20card%20that%20is%20charging%2018%25%2C%20repaying%20that%20credit%20card%20debt%20is%20the%20equivalent%20of%20earning%20an%2018%25%20rate%20of%20return.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-recession-economy-personal-finance-economic-crash-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741507261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb3155b8b41a9673fa0484%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-prepare-for-recession-economy-personal-finance-economic-crash-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whether%20the%20economy%20is%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20a%20recession%20or%20already%20in%20one%2C%20it's%20important%20not%20to%20panic%20as%20you%20make%20decisions%20about%20your%20money%2C%20job%2C%20or%20investments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A57%2C