E%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%20lighthouse%20keeper%20is%20also%20a%20physically%20demanding%20job%20for%20Rosenberg.%20He's%20often%20alone%20carrying%20heavy%20building%20materials%20to%20the%20island%20across%20treacherous%20terrain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhere%20I%20launch%20the%20boat%20and%20land%20the%20boat%2C%20they're%20very%20slippery%2C%20the%20crossing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223520%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Matt%20Rosenberg%20takes%20a%20selfie%20while%20paddling%20to%20the%20Nubble%20lighthouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cc8fb069253ccddf98b31d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221980%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESeveral%20times%20a%20week%20after%20school%2C%20Rosenberg%20will%20launch%20his%20white%20rowboat%20to%20Nubble%20lighthouse%20on%20an%20island%20just%20off%20the%20mainland.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Rosenberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERosenberg's%20job%20is%20only%20seasonal%20from%20April%20through%20January%20because%20weather%20conditions%20off%20the%20island%20become%20unpredictable.%20Waves%20reach%20heights%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Facs.evsc.virginia.edu%2Fnoreasters%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eover%2020%20feet%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20Nor'easter%20storms%20in%20March%20and%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPower%20lines%20are%20probably%2070%20feet%20above%20the%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rosenberg.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20those%20taken%20out%20by%20the%20energy%20from%20the%20waves%20when%20they%20hit%20the%20shore%20and%20then%20go%20up%20into%20the%20power%20lines%20and%20twist%20them%20up%20and%20tear%20them%20down.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8f73140-a605-4e04-9e84-fde3a2bb040e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20he%20loves%20lighthouse%20keeping%20so%20much%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20challenges%20of%20being%20a%20lighthouse%20worker%2C%20Rosenberg%20loves%20his%20job%20and%20wants%20to%20continue%20for%20the%20next%20decade%20into%20his%20sixties%2C%20as%20long%20as%20he's%20physically%20able.%20He%20is%20paid%20%2421%20an%20hour%20to%20maintain%20the%20popular%20tourist%20attraction%2C%20a%20duty%20he%20describes%20as%20a%20labor%20of%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20jobs%20bring%20you%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2051-year-old.%20%26quot%3BThis%20job%20brings%20you%20peace%2C%20because%20you're%20spending%20so%20much%20time%20in%20a%20beautiful%20place%20by%20yourself.%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20occasionally%20sees%20wildlife%20from%20a%2020-foot%20basking%20shark%20to%20a%20pregnant%20doe%20giving%20birth%20on%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20seal%20rests%20on%20the%20shore%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Nubble%20lighthouse.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cc966469253ccddf98b364%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222494%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERosenberg%20sees%20seal%20pups%20and%20adults%20year-round%20and%20volunteers%20with%20Marine%20Mammals%20of%20Maine%20to%20respond%20when%20animals%20are%20sick%20or%20injured.%3Cp%3EMatt%20Rosenberg%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAutonomy%20and%20self-reliance%20are%20big%20parts%20of%20Rosenberg's%20daily%20life.%20He's%20proud%20to%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20tradition%20of%20Nubble%20Lighthouse%20stewards%20from%20its%20earliest%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20didn't%20have%20running%20water%2C%20they%20didn't%20have%20modern%20heat%20at%20that%20early%20in%20the%20lighthouse's%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20Rosenberg%20said.%20%26quot%3BLighthouse%20keepers%20of%20that%20day%20were%20also%20the%20primary%20rescue%20squad%20for%20the%20vicinity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Victorian-style%2C%20white-painted%20lighthouse%20with%20its%20gingerbread%20trim%20around%20the%20eaves%20stands%20out%20on%20the%20shore%2C%20a%20stalwart%20reminder%20of%20the%