C%20I%20experienced%20the%20balance%20of%20having%20a%20career%20without%20missing%20important%20moments%20with%20my%20kids.%20Managing%20twins%20is%20tough%2C%20especially%20while%20in%20a%20senior%20role%2C%20but%20I%20realised%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20to%20have%20both%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikita%20Agarwal%20has%20an%20equally%20impressive%20educational%20and%20career%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20a%20background%20in%20business%20development%20and%20supply%20chain%2C%20I%20worked%20with%20e-commerce%20giants%20like%20ShopClues%20and%20OverCart%2C%20as%20well%20as%20renowned%20brands%20like%20Tata%20Motors%20and%20Hyundai.%20After%20taking%20a%20step%20back%20to%20focus%20on%20motherhood%2C%20I%20realised%20it%20was%20time%20to%20return.%20Entrepreneurship%20is%20in%20my%20DNA%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20building%20something%20meaningful%20was%20the%20next%20natural%20step%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPersonal%20struggles%20that%20led%20to%20TwinsTribe%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBound%20by%20their%20shared%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F349527%2Fnew-mothers-online-support-groups-postpartum-breastfeeding-formula-sleep-training-parenting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20experience%20of%20motherhood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20sisters%20decided%20to%20join%20forces%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20launch%20of%20TwinsTribe%20in%202023.%20The%20platform%20is%20designed%20to%20connect%20twin%20parents%2C%20providing%20them%20with%20a%20supportive%20community%20as%20well%20as%20products%20tailored%20to%20their%20unique%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20for%20TwinsTribe%20emerged%20from%20the%20personal%20challenges%20Ruchika%20faced%20while%20raising%20her%20twins.%20The%20lack%20of%20suitable%20products%20for%20twin%20parents%2C%20like%20strollers%20that%20could%20fit%20into%20tight%20spaces%2C%20prompted%20her%20to%20think%20about%20suitable%20solutions.%20%E2%80%9CLiving%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20detachable%20stroller%20for%20my%20twins%20that%20was%20compact%20enough%20to%20fit%20in%20narrow%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2040-year-old%20mother%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20thing%20I%20realised%20was%20that%20twin%20parenting%20is%20different%20from%20single%20parenting.%20For%20instance%2C%20many%20people%20advise%20parents%20to%20sleep%20when%20the%20baby%20sleeps%2C%20but%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20feasible%20for%20twin%20parents%2C%20as%20they%20rarely%20sleep%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20second%20challenge%20is%20the%20struggle%20with%20exclusive%20breastfeeding%20for%20twins.%20Most%20twin%20mothers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20milk%20supply%20to%20nourish%20both%20babies%2C%20and%20even%20if%20they%20do%2C%20the%20process%20of%20breastfeeding%20two%20babies%20is%20physically%20and%20emotionally%20draining.%20This%20often%20leads%20to%20twin%20mothers%20experiencing%20postpartum%20blues%20or%20even%20depression%20due%20to%20the%20overwhelming%20demands.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20they%20need%20support%20from%20fellow%20twin%20parents%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-21-at-09.30.06-4_11zon-1740921702-500x667.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20twin%20stroller%20by%20TwinsTribe%20is%20their%20star%20product%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22http